":"其實係想迫自己練琴同有個目標 以前就係學下玩下但之後覺得練琴好煩就冇再學 依家成日上網睇人彈琴覺得好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T20:36:31.000Z","msg":"樂器無得急於求成架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n練返好基本功先<br />\n唔練點彈點發揮得好啲樂曲<br />\n練琴唔可以停 btw要剪指甲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n彈classic盡量唔好用電子琴"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T22:47:42.000Z","msg":"唔鍾意留指甲 無急於求成吖淨係問考級大約要幾耐 俾個目標同時間自己"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T05:29:04.000Z","msg":"無得講要幾耐<br />\n不過你有底應該會易過新手嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一般都係一跳就考3級<br />\n範圍係scales, pieces, sight readings同oral<br />\nPieces有3首要彈，指定樂曲<br />\n<em><span class=\"gold\">A樂曲通常係巴洛克到古典時期早段<br />\nB樂曲通常係古典時期中後段到浪漫時期早段<br />\nC樂曲就係浪漫時期後段到Contemporary <br />\n<a href=\"http://eweb.tmups.tp.edu.tw/module/download/update/mus03/file1951_9.doc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Feweb.tmups.tp.edu.tw%2Fmodule%2Fdownload%2Fupdate%2Fmus03%2Ffile1951_9.doc&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmcIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=d03532d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://eweb.tmups.tp.edu.tw/module/download/update/mus03/file1951_9.doc</a><br />\n</span></em><br />\n練到咁上下搵啲考試譜睇下覺得hand唔handle到<br />\n如果得咪可以去報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n考完可以彈下唔同時期嘅作品 <br />\n通常啲琴行有好多黃色嘅琴書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你問下佢依家自己幾多級應該買邊啲<br />\n買佢推介果啲就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以跟曲種買合集<br />\n例如係sonatina, sonata(因為多到數唔曬，唔會彈後完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n其他嘅可以跟返唔同作曲家買唔同樂譜<br />\n例如係bach嘅2 part/3part inventions, fugues<br />\n唔同作曲家嘅練習曲<br />\nChopin嘅waltz 等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25ac5555c9dc36efadfdacc7ad5109466f985232","tid":2227461,"uid":301263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"